Leonid Kinskey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leonid_Kinskey 0 Leonid Kinskey (c. 1894or 18 April 1903 – 8 September 1998) was a Russian-born film and television actor who enjoyed a long career. Kinskey is best known for his role as Sascha in the film Casablanca (1942).
